   RandPlaylistBuilder For Android
			  
		Borys H.N.
		3.11.13
		
=====================================
	
Instructions:
1) Proceed to choose a playlist, or you can create a shuffle
2) Uncheck songs you don't want to play
3) Selected a song, and press play to start the playlist

